    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Auth-sensitive code (ADR-028 binding); Code Page is the only surface that imports `@spaarke/auth` directly; misconfiguration would cause popup-loops or token-acquisition failures. FULL rigor + code-review + adr-check at Step 9.5.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
